videos.description: Tremont Waters puts it up for Marlon Taylor who slams it home with a huge two-handed dunk for LSU.
videos.headline: Taylor pounds home huge alley-oop for LSU

videos.description: Marlon Taylor picks up a pass that was almost picked off by a Georgia defender and converts it into a two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Taylor converts with big dunk off of bad pass

videos.description: The Bulldog's Jordan Harris sneaks around a defender and grabs the pass from Nicolas Claxton to bring home a one-handed jam.
videos.headline: Harris skirts between defenders for dunk
